flowchart LR
  S[Canonical state: certified global section]
  Q[Dirty-cell trigger index and scheduler]
  R[Execute enabled local rules]
  P[Stage local proposals]
  J[Merge writes through stalk algebras]
  X[Propagate affected restrictions]
  C[Check covers, overlaps, and anchors]
  G{Global section certified?}
  O[Typed obstruction]
  N[Commit one new section revision]
  T{Terminal predicate}
  F[Final output and committed effects]
  K[Topology-bound checkpoint]

  S --> Q
  Q --> R
  R --> P
  P --> J
  J --> X
  X --> C
  C --> G
  G -->|no| O
  G -->|yes| N
  N --> S
  S --> T
  T -->|continue| Q
  T -->|done| F
  S -. checkpoint / resume .-> K
